[XSMM] libxsmm ukernel backend (#223)
* [XSMM] libxsmm ukernel backend
Adds libxsmm as a new XSMM ukernel target for CPU lowering. Initial lowering covers basic support for FP32 and BF16 data types across different extensions and architectures.
Summary of changes: - Extends ukernel handle creator to allow reuse for both backends - Adds prebuilt libxsmm as an optional external build dependency - Adds XSMM runtime and lowering pass
